{"tid":1864130,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"3m 冷氣機隔塵網自製口罩有冇得諗","createTime":"2020-02-05T12:35:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-17T07:36:32.000Z","uid":64131,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"6b3920a1c8d89a9c0fe106a2d38ab56a0e4274f3","tid":1864130,"uid":64131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T12:35:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pFCMKeq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpFCMKeq.png&h=9551d9af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n外層: 不織布<br />\n中層: 隔塵網<br />\n內層: 紗布<br />\n<br />\n加兩條橡筋<br />\n開個衣車車埋搞掂"},{"pid":"e6cde88578a7980d73c5f0ae1f2967fbf0fc9705","tid":1864130,"uid":58147,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T12:40:58.000Z","msg":"睇圖片個網啲窿都幾大吓。"},{"pid":"38f67092ba7b1c23d1206ce3234337f21e6b06bf","tid":1864130,"uid":265839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T12:42:35.000Z","msg":"原理同N95 相同，但係過濾到幾多um ?"},{"pid":"960f4e73225b1c9cdaac87366d4d7770a38b72a4","tid":1864130,"uid":96431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T12:44:17.000Z","msg":"隔塵網準備賣斷市<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4689c0b818682ddf8f5fc1755ac851058443ecf2","tid":1864130,"uid":41988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T12:46:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ShwmybX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FShwmybX.png&h=122107f4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"698377bc106411055616e100b8caf59b1ab38d0a","tid":1864130,"uid":23511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T12:55:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/personal/%E8%87%AA%E5%AE%B6%E8%A3%BD%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9-%E5%88%B0%E5%BA%95%E6%9C%89%E6%B2%92%E6%9C%89%E7%94%A8/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpersonal%2F%25E8%2587%25AA%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E8%25A3%25BD%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9-%25E5%2588%25B0%25E5%25BA%2595%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%25B2%2592%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%2594%25A8%2F&d=SLV77eIUGxkMmCzjf2iSt3lPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=8de76a03\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpersonal%2F%25E8%2587%25AA%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E8%25A3%25BD%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9-%25E5%2588%25B0%25E5%25BA%2595%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%25B2%2592%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%2594%25A8%2F&h=7787bfaa\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/personal/%E8%87%AA%E5%AE%B6%E8%A3%BD%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9-%E5%88%B0%E5%BA%95%E6%9C%89%E6%B2%92%E6%9C%89%E7%94%A8/</a><br />\n<br />\n有得選擇，就用手術口罩。沒得選擇，才用自家製口罩。<br />\n自家製的口罩防護力雖然較低，但有戴總比沒戴好。<br />\n任何種類的口罩，都要保持乾爽，如果濕了，就要換，否則更易中招。<br />\n自家製口罩，兩層棉及一層棉相比，兩層棉會有更好的防護力，雖然加起來都及不上手術用口罩。<br />\n如果要自製口罩，根據文中提及的研究，選擇材料上，棉質較好，亞麻布較差，絲質最差。另外，這份研究也提及，用全新的吸塵機的過濾袋做口罩，防護效果跟手術口罩非常接近。<br />\n口罩要貼面，才有良好的保護效果。<br />\n口罩不是萬能，還要配合：病者隔離，咳嗽或打噴嚏時要注意禮節，時常保持手部清潔，才能達到最佳的防護效果。"},{"pid":"8a1eeb461c1ed8fab32cacc329e39a42e6426efc","tid":1864130,"uid":64131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38f67092ba7b1c23d1206ce3234337f21e6b06bf","tid":1864130,"uid":265839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T12:42:35.000Z","msg":"原理同N95 相同，但係過濾到幾多um ?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T13:01:53.000Z","msg":"pm 2.5<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AAkba3z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAAkba3z.png&h=d1ff1b91&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"99c084b882eb54c653f7b9f605ab51aa99bff725","tid":1864130,"uid":173951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T13:03:14.000Z","msg":"我做野的鋪頭有賣呢款<br />\n二月開始d客一買買幾卷呢d 好恐怖"},{"pid":"fd20e214432680bcce6948626b4776c43d962ddb","tid":1864130,"uid":173951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T13:03:27.000Z","msg":"平時一卷可以用一至兩個月"},{"p